window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Star baseball player Bishop Henson was Bailey Landon's biggest crush—until every interaction with him leaves her believing that he's nothing but a playboy. Unfortunately, she keeps running into the infuriatingly handsome athlete at every turn. But she has bigger issues, including figuring out a way to save her family's farm. Right now, she doesn't need the complications that come with a relationship, and she's not about to risk her heart to the local baseball team's celebrity shortstop.</p> <p>At least that's what she thought.</p> <p>It turns out, there might be more to baseball's biggest player than meets the eye. Can Bishop change Bailey's mind about him? Or will these two opposites strike out in the game of love?</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
